    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="matlab笔记"><a href="#matlab笔记" class="headerlink" title="matlab笔记"></a><strong>matlab笔记</strong></h1><h3 id="matlab的数据操作——变量和语句"><a href="#matlab的数据操作——变量和语句" class="headerlink" title="matlab的数据操作——变量和语句"></a>matlab的数据操作——变量和语句</h3><p>1、变量命名</p><p>字母开头，包括字母、数字、下划线，区分大小写</p><p>不声明，不定义，拿来即用。</p><p>2、语句</p><p>回车则表示一句结束，末尾无分号，则输出该句执行的结果，有分号只执行不输出。</p><p>注释以%开头表示       <a id="more"></a></p><p>一行写不开，用……（英文输入法）续写，否则默认这一句已经完毕。</p><p>3、赋值</p><p>变量=表达式</p><p>表达式</p><p>前者将表达式的值赋值给=前的变量，后者将表达式的值赋值给默认变量ans。//没定义默认为ans？</p><h3 id="matlab的数据操作——变量管理"><a href="#matlab的数据操作——变量管理" class="headerlink" title="matlab的数据操作——变量管理"></a>matlab的数据操作——变量管理</h3><p>1、工作空间中驻留的变量查看</p><p>who</p><p>whos</p><p>2、删除 </p><p>clear</p><p>3、保存</p><p>save</p><p><strong>plot()    二维线图 函数</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">eg:  y&#x3D;[2, 3, 4, 5];</span><br><span class="line">            plot(y)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">eg:  x&#x3D;[3, 4, 8, 12];</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">y&#x3D;sin(x);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">plot(x,y)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>快速注释： ctrl + alt  </p><p>函数参数可调标识变量 ：  nargin    nargout   varargin   varargout      前两者为输入输出参数<strong>个数</strong>，后面两个可以代表未知的输入输出变量。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">eg:  fuction re &#x3D; add_multi(a,b,c,d)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">if nargin &#x3D;&#x3D;4</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">re &#x3D;……;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">elseif nargin  &#x3D;&#x3D;3</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">re&#x3D;……;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">else </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">……</span><br><span class="line">end</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出= 函数（输入变量）</p>]]></content>
    
